# API Design And Versioning

- Use explicit versioning (`/api/v{version}` or equivalent version header strategy).
- Keep contracts backward compatible within a version.
- Use resource-oriented URIs and consistent HTTP semantics.
- Validate request DTOs and return meaningful problem details payloads.

## Example

```csharp
// Good: explicit versioning + typed result
[ApiVersion("1.0")]
[Route("api/v{version:apiVersion}/orders")]
public sealed class OrdersController : ControllerBase {}
```
